Deflection				KEY:Vow of Poverty ~ Deflection						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural						DEFINE:VowOfPovertyDeflectionBonus|0		DESC:A 6th-level ascetic receives a +1 deflection bonus to his Armor Class. This bonus increases to +2 at 12th level, and to +3 at 18th level.																																																																																																							BONUS:COMBAT|AC|VowOfPovertyDeflectionBonus|TYPE=Deflection												BONUS:VAR|VowOfPovertyDeflectionBonus|1|PREPCLEVEL:MIN=6	BONUS:VAR|VowOfPovertyDeflectionBonus|1|PREPCLEVEL:MIN=12	BONUS:VAR|VowOfPovertyDeflectionBonus|1|PREPCLEVEL:MIN=18																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.30	BENEFIT:Deflection Bonus to AC +%1|VowOfPovertyDeflectionBonus
